Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上个月 为庆祝我们的一周年\NSo last month,to celebrate our one year of dating bliss,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dave给我了个惊喜 带我去了 Huey Lewis and The News演唱会\NBig Dave surprised me and took me on a Huey Lewis and The News cruise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.70,0:00:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第七首安可曲"Hip To Be Square"的时候\NCut to seventh encore "Hip To Be Square,"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huey把我拉上舞台\NHuey pulls me up on le stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的事你打死也想不到\NYou'll never guess what happened next.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我的上衣掉了 - 她自己脱的\N- My top came off! - She took it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能直视\NUgh! Gross,mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她风韵犹存噢 - 真的吗\N- She's a keeper. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huey Lewis他们都直立了\NHuey Lewis and them thangs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你问起\NSo in answer to your question,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的咪咪第二次被一堆人看\Nthat was the second largest crowd to ever see my hooters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那第一次是什么时候\NOoh! What was the first?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Robert Bork的听证会 - 92年硕士毕业\N- Robert Bork's confirmation hearing. - The '92 Masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你俩说的可不一样 - 等等\N- You said one thing,you said another thing. - Oh,wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是第三次吗 - 演唱会是第三次\N- Ooh,is that the third? - Cruise was third.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好吧 这是第三次 - 是的\N- Okay,that was the third. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起出去玩 我们玩点什么好呢\NSpeaking of things hanging out,how about us,huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸和Penny的妈妈都在\NWe've got my dad here,we've got Penny's mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在了 太好了\Nthe whole crew. This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 想不通为什么有人觉得\NI know. I don't know why anybody thought
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们约会很奇怪\Nit was weird you guys were dating at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们超般配 像Jay和Bey那么般配\NYou are great together-- Jay and Bey great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不懂你在说什么 - 她是说Jay-Z和Beyonce\N- Don't know what that is. - She means Jay-Z and Beyonce.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我在Chesapeake湾的朋友Jay\NNot my friend Jay in the Chesapeake Bay...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在那溺水身亡了\N'cause that's where he drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:00:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安息吧 Jay\NRIP,Jay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潮水拥你入怀 地狱唤你回家\NEmbraced by the tide and called home to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么湾\NAny-bay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多人 明天干嘛好呢\Nwhat are we gonna do with this big group tomorrow,huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4对4斗牛?\NA little 4-on-4 hoops?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八人欢乐单车 要不舞个龙?\NMaybe an 8-person party bike? Chinese New Year dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.29,0:01:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我们打算带Penny和Dave\NWell,actually,we're taking Penny and Dave
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去科技馆看"电视机器人发展史"\Nto that "TV Robots Through The Ages" exhibit... at the Museum of Science.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.86,0:01:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是好东西\NIt covers all the greats.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰森一家里的Rosie\NThey got Rosie from "The Jetsons,"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.38,0:01:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霹雳游侠里的KITT 还有Angie Harmon\NKITT from "Knight Rider," Angie Harmon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们四个怎么办\NWhat about this foursome over here,huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jane Brad Alex 我们几个干什么好\NJane? Brad? Alex? What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.07,0:01:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舞个迷你龙吗\N4-person mini dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.47,0:01:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听起来不错 不过我们得去割礼\NUh,we would love to,but we have to go to a bris.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.43,0:01:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 去什么 - 就是犹太割礼的聚会\N- A what? - It is a Jewish circumcision party.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 只有那个婴儿会受割礼\NDon't worry. Only the baby gets circumcised.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩得开心 看好小弟\NAll right,well,have fun. And mind your groin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.31,0:01:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来大家都有\NOkay,so everybody's got...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安排了 挺好的\Ngot stuff to do. That's-- that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就先这样 然后再...\NWe'll put a pin in it, and then-- and then we'll all... get...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等大家有空再聚\Nget back together w-when-- when everyone's schedule permits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看着不太高兴\NThis is not a great color on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你们总聚在一起挺可爱的\NWell,I think it's adorable how much time you guys spend together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:01:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整天黏在一起\NYou're practically attached at the hip,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像"真体育"里的德国连体妓女\Nlike those conjoined German prostitutes I saw on "Real Sports."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是举重选手\NThey're also power lifters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不觉得我们黏在一起\NI wouldn't say we spend that much time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过是一星期的四五次早餐\NI mean,just breakfast four or five times a week before work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多每天小酌几次\NAnd drinks during the day most days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.70,0:02:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也没有每天 不过每晚是肯定的\NNot every day,but definitely every evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新八卦都要当面传达\NAnd,sure,we always deliver news in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许这点要重新考虑下\NYou know,maybe we should review that policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jane 你知道Max跟谁搞上了吗\NJane,did you hear who Max hooked up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个叫Jorsh的人\NA guy named Jorsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能稍后再谈吗\NUm,can it wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jane 你听说....\NJane! Did you hear what I--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jorsh亲娘 这真不是闹着玩的\NDear Jorsh. That thing is no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.53,0:02:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是不懂为啥你要看我的检查表\NI still don't know why you felt the need to read my chart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家总说 得看看别人的想法\NJane,they say you should always get a second opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是我自己的比较恶心罢了\NMine just happens to be gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是啊 - 说得没错\N- Yeah,it is. - You got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但感觉不错\NBut it feels so good.
